
- Register digiKam so that it can be run when one plug a usb mass storage or a camera.
- Install only the needed files not the whole kde4. Set a list of unnecessary files provided by KDE-windows installer.

- Add digiKam's icon modified with an arrow to the installer.
- Add digiKam's icon modifier with an arrow in the opposite direction to the uninstaller.
- Add digiKam's logo in the uninstaller welcome page.
- Add RELEASENOTES list on installer.

